lementation, and interpretation of results.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 30. Aug 2021) 4adiagnostic algorithms. 4aquality assurance. 4astandardization. 7aMEDICAL / Laboratory Medicine.2bisacsh1 aAufenanger, Johannes, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aAufenanger, Johannes, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aBrödje, Dörte.1 aDegel, Fritz.1 aDesel, Herbert.1 aEckardstein, Arnold.1 aEhrich, Jochen H.H.1 aFelgenhauer, Norbert.1 aGuder, Walter G.1 aHallbach, Jürgen.1 aHoffmann, Georg, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHoffmann, Georg, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aHofmann, Oliver.1 aHofmann, Walter, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aImöhl, Matthias, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aImöhl, Matthias.1 aKeller, Frieder.1 aMinder, Elisabeth .1 aPoland, Julia.1 aRenz, Harald.1 aSchambeck, Christian Martin.1 aScherberich, Jürgen E.1 aSeufferlein, Thomas.1 aSiech, Marco.1 aStachon, Axel, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aStachon, Axel.1 aWick, Manfred Wolfgang.1 aYagmur, Eray.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2016z978311070100508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2016z9783110485103oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Medicine and Life Sciences 2016z9783110485295oZDB-23-DPM0 cEPUBz97831104538980 cprintz978311045367640uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311045508340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110455083423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783110455083.jpg  a978-3-11-070100-5  DG Plus eBook-Package 2016b2016  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_MDPM